{"tid":1391776,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"728被打總督察確定為前一哥鄧竟成個仔","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:21:22.000Z","uid":68738,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ae94d6ede23fb66cbf3a87c4b3f9a9dc4d2c2295","tid":1391776,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3104222/org/c6d37545fce9c110979d9eb213d86a97.jpg/gIQz4LAqqRJV-ZLiZ8skrFCiFvOvnKLWIf5YlCH-WJQ?v=w960r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3104222%2Forg%2Fc6d37545fce9c110979d9eb213d86a97.jpg%2FgIQz4LAqqRJV-ZLiZ8skrFCiFvOvnKLWIf5YlCH-WJQ%3Fv%3Dw960r16_9&h=5f933f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3103948/org/a9b5d37cecba5be3308c00f81f95da90.jpg/trD5y8ByhOligOaMvYw5ewOl1GSmvxExVenc6FXp3Og?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3103948%2Forg%2Fa9b5d37cecba5be3308c00f81f95da90.jpg%2FtrD5y8ByhOligOaMvYw5ewOl1GSmvxExVenc6FXp3Og%3Fv%3Dw960&h=273b0808&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總督察鄧智兆(中)是前「一哥」鄧竟成的兒子。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n鄧智兆理大畢業後投考警隊<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，鄧智兆為鄧竟成的幼子，畢業於理工大學工程學系，他在2007年投考警隊，畢業時成績優異，獲施禮榮盾、榮譽警棍的獎項。<br />\n<br />\n不過，鄧智兆於2010年因調查上水一宗刑事毁壞案，而被傳召上庭作供時遲到逾3小時，遭裁判官斥他早獲出庭通知，卻未有依時到庭，更遭當面質疑「有咩特權可以唔嚟？」鄧智兆當時被裁判官接連訓斥，只能連番致歉。"},{"pid":"a330db3aa91681551117eceffdf275354c9326b8","tid":1391776,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:14:19.000Z","msg":"特權"},{"pid":"2acfd65330518e77238f3e98ea4627983ff33fce","tid":1391776,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:15:35.000Z","msg":"點打呀 , 靠屈"},{"pid":"748438e903868aee728eb6bd54a76242b9fb27aa","tid":1391776,"uid":293227,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:15:41.000Z","msg":"你最好唔好比我見到你放工"},{"pid":"dbec6ecc0ad3edbb2dc91f61950489136e82e62c","tid":1391776,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月3日 旺角遊行<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"b5754cc2642e607ebc0fcdab1c7b358273b6292d","tid":1391776,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/__kgij7SxsHY/TFt2qEDr1bI/AAAAAAAACic/Fj1OQWbzg4E/s1600/Police%201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F__kgij7SxsHY%2FTFt2qEDr1bI%2FAAAAAAAACic%2FFj1OQWbzg4E%2Fs1600%2FPolice%25201.jpg&h=f67a9b22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4868c802abaefd4bbdeed8c42f3739b197699308","tid":1391776,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:21:22.000Z","msg":"距離午飯休庭時間尚餘 15分鐘，控方欲傳召有份調查本案的鄧智兆督察作供，卻發覺他原來未到庭等候。署任暫委裁判官余焯文即時語帶不滿地謂：「佢有乜嘢特權可以唔準時嚟？」<br />\n<br />\n主控官解釋，鄧智兆正在附近的上水警署候命，步程約需五分鐘，建議法庭稍為押後聆訊，惟裁判官堅持要他立即出庭解釋。 <br />\n<br />\n約五分鐘後，西裝筆挺的鄧智兆抵達法庭。開庭後，他向裁判官解釋自己正在放大假。由於上級指有案件需與他商討，遂要他返回駐守的上水警署。他又謂：「控方律師叫我 stand by（候命），咁啱差館有嘢做，我咪返去囉。」 <br />\n<br />\n我爸是鄧竟成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}